            <title><![CDATA[【#为何中年人睡眠那么少# [衰]】#老人白天总打盹正常吗# 儿童或青少年时期睡眠时间长是因为身体和智力生长发育需要。随着人体发育成熟，所需要的生理睡眠时间就...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E9%82%A3%E4%B9%88%E5%B0%91%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E9%82%A3%E4%B9%88%E5%B0%91%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#为何中年人睡眠那么少#</span></a> <span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BD%E5%A4%A9%E6%80%BB%E6%89%93%E7%9B%B9%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BD%E5%A4%A9%E6%80%BB%E6%89%93%E7%9B%B9%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#老人白天总打盹正常吗#</span></a> 儿童或青少年时期睡眠时间长是因为身体和智力生长发育需要。随着人体发育成熟，所需要的生理睡眠时间就趋向平稳或下降。到了55岁或60岁以后，睡眠时间又开始延长，这和睡眠质量下降和睡眠连续性的破坏有关。55岁或60岁以后的人群白天容易疲惫、困倦，下午也会经常打盹，这样反复打盹、短睡的时间积累在一起，总的睡眠时间是相对延长的👇🏻<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4896541543170137" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视网的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/003z5L7fly8hdip52lo3hj60o00diq4h02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/KxcdUrqylx0855OlPa6c010412015u4s0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=864x486.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1683004709&amp;ssig=BWh3FxUpzc&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/976I0NyPlx0855OlT72U01041200NCr70E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1683004709&amp;ssig=ABlO1jnkQ7&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/a1noutozlx0855OlnIT601041200vpsM0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1683004709&amp;ssig=1ZHB%2FXXFoU&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4896541543170137&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
